question: Which among the following cities of Maharashtra was rated five star by the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affair's program of Star Rating of Garbage Free Cities 2019-20?
explanation: Navi Mumbai was rated five star by the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affair's program of Star Rating of Garbage Free Cities 2019-20. The other cities of India with five-star rating are Ambikapur, Rajkot, Surat, Mysuru, Indore.
